<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:16:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>极右翼希望欧盟拥有更多权力以反映可能的选举收益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hard-right-wants-more-eu-power-reflect-likely-election-gains-2024-05-06/</link><description>法国右翼议员让·保罗·加罗 (Jean-Paul Garraud) 的办公室位于远处的附楼，他的目标是更接近欧洲议会决策中心的地方。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:02:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hard-right-wants-more-eu-power-reflect-likely-election-gains-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>低预算的中国游客凸显香港旅游业的转变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-budget-chinese-travellers-highlight-shift-hong-kong-tourism-2024-05-06/</link><description>注重成本的中国游客已经取代了许多曾经涌入香港的现金充裕的内地游客，其中一些人只对免费步行游览这座城市以及在深圳过夜以省钱感兴趣。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 05:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-budget-chinese-travellers-highlight-shift-hong-kong-tourism-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国的关税可能会给干邑制造商留下过多的白兰地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-tariffs-could-leave-cognac-makers-with-too-much-brandy-2024-05-06/</link><description>根据路透社的计算，分析师和担心企业可能被迫打折的投资者认为，中国对欧盟白兰地征收高额关税将使法国公司拥有大量白兰地，而这些白兰地可能很难在其他地方出售。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 05:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-tariffs-could-leave-cognac-makers-with-too-much-brandy-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和美国在年度军事演习中击退模拟外国入侵者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-repel-mock-foreign-invaders-annual-military-exercises-2024-05-06/</link><description>周一，美国和菲律宾武装部队发射导弹和大炮，阻止模拟入侵菲律宾面向台湾的北部海域，在地区紧张局势升级之际展示军事力量并加强关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 04:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-repel-mock-foreign-invaders-annual-military-exercises-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国和美国电动汽车的增长，今年汽油需求增长将放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gasoline-demand-growth-slow-this-year-ev-growth-china-us-2024-05-06/</link><description>分析师表示，受中国和美国转向电动汽车以及去年 COVID-19 疫情爆发后恢复正常消费的推动，全球汽油需求增长可能会在 2024 年减半，从而挤压下半年炼油厂的利润率。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:23:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gasoline-demand-growth-slow-this-year-ev-growth-china-us-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示不会加剧南海紧张局势，不会使用高压水枪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-wont-raise-south-china-sea-tensions-wont-use-water-cannons-2024-05-06/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，该国不会在南海使用高压水枪或任何进攻性武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:20:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-wont-raise-south-china-sea-tensions-wont-use-water-cannons-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因中国股市上涨而上涨，美联储削减押注；日元走弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-06/</link><description>由于市场重新押注美联储今年很可能放松利率，亚洲股市周一升至一年多来的最高水平，而日元在上周因东京疑似货币干预而大幅飙升后走弱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国服务业活动有所放缓，但仍保持稳健</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-eases-april-still-solid-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-05-06/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，由于成本上升，中国服务业活动扩张略有放缓，但新订单增长加速，商业信心稳步上升，提振了经济持续复苏的希望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 01:53:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-eases-april-still-solid-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>美元因新的降息押注而保持稳定；日元本周开局不利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-after-soft-us-jobs-report-yen-starts-week-back-foot-2024-05-06/</link><description>美元周一大体稳定，因疲软的美国就业报告提振了美联储今年可能仍可能降息的押注，而日元在上周疑似干预行动助长了疯狂上涨后大幅走低。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 01:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-after-soft-us-jobs-report-yen-starts-week-back-foot-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：金融状况亮起绿灯，外汇平静</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 21:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>库尔最后时刻的进球为中央海岸赢得了亚足联杯决赛的胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/late-kuol-strike-earns-central-coast-victory-final-afc-cup-2024-05-05/</link><description>周日，中央海岸水手队在马斯喀特苏丹卡布斯体育场以 1-0 战胜黎巴嫩阿尔阿赫德队，成为第一支赢得亚足联杯冠军的澳大利亚俱乐部。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:45:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/late-kuol-strike-earns-central-coast-victory-final-afc-cup-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国队击败印度尼西亚队夺得汤姆斯杯和尤伯杯双冠王</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/china-down-indonesia-claim-thomas-uber-cup-double-2024-05-05/</link><description>中国男队在周日的两项比赛中夺得尤伯杯冠军，印尼队获得亚军，时隔六年后，中国男队重新夺回汤姆斯杯冠军。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 15:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/china-down-indonesia-claim-thomas-uber-cup-double-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司的布鲁克斯跑步首席执行官将中国和欧洲视为增长领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/berkshires-brooks-running-ceo-sees-china-europe-growth-areas-2024-05-05/</link><description>布鲁克斯跑步公司的新任首席执行官表示，这家由沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司拥有的跑鞋制造商将中国和欧洲视为该公司在美国创收最多的业务的增长领域</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 10:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/berkshires-brooks-running-ceo-sees-china-europe-growth-areas-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>马克龙准备谈贸易之际，中国习近平赞扬法国关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/frances-macron-set-press-visiting-xi-trade-ukraine-2024-05-05/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周日抵达巴黎，在与欧盟贸易争端日益加剧的背景下进行罕见访问，称赞中法关系是国际典范。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 00:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/frances-macron-set-press-visiting-xi-trade-ukraine-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔股东拒绝气候、多元化、中国提案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/berkshire-shareholders-reject-climate-diversity-china-proposals-2024-05-04/</link><description>周六，伯克希尔哈撒韦公司股东以压倒性多数否决了沃伦·巴菲特集团解决环境和社会政策问题的六项提案，这位亿万富翁投资者及其董事会都反对所有这些提案。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 21:52:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/berkshire-shareholders-reject-climate-diversity-china-proposals-2024-05-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>